ygData.messageBody:
Hail Fellow EQ Sister!

I play Rain D'Terrah on Tarew Marr - Level 26 Warrior. I look forward to
hearing and corresponding with all of EQ Women for some fun talk and shared
resources.

Rain

-----Original Message-----
From: Heather Hire <hrootbeer@...>
To: EQ_women@onelist.com <EQ_women@onelist.com>
Date: Wednesday, June 16, 1999 9:32 AM
Subject: Re: [EQ_women] Welcome to EQ_women@onelist.com


>From: Heather Hire <hrootbeer@...>
>
>Hello everyone. My character is Genneth an 14th level bard half-elf,
>and I also play a 4th level Erudite enchantress, Erealua both on the
>Tunare server. I liked the idea of this EQ women's list and look
>forward to the discussions and insites we all have regarding the game.
>
>Heather
>
>
>--- EQ_women-owner@onelist.com wrote:
>> Hi there, and welcome to EQ Women! This mailing
>> list is
>> for women who play the game Everquest to meet
>> eachother
>> and chat.
>>
>> Please feel free to post an intro message with your
>> character's name, race, class, level and server
>> (and anything else you'd like).
>> For example:
>>
>> "Hi everyone! I play Iuna, a 17th level wood elf
>> druid
>> on Mithaniel Marr. I'm looking forward to
>> chatting on the list."
>>
>> If you ever want to unsubscribe, go to the ONElist
>> web site, at
>> www.onelist.com, and select the User Center link
>> from the menu bar
>> on the left. This menu will also let you change your
>> subscription
>> between digest and normal mode. This list is for
>> women only, so please respect this policy and
>> unsubscribe if you
>> are not a woman!.
>>
>> Have fun,
>>
>> Christina
>>
